sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser /stats
    participant N as Next.js API
    participant G as Gateway

    B->>B: useEffect — status=authenticated?
    B->>B: fetchAllData() — Promise.allSettled

    par 3 fetches en paralelo
        B->>N: GET /api/analytics/stats
        N->>N: getServerSession() + check ADMIN_EMAIL
        alt No admin
            N-->>B: 403 Forbidden
            B->>B: setForbidden(true)
        else Es admin
            N->>G: GET /analytics/stats (Bearer)
            G-->>N: UserStats JSON
            N-->>B: UserStats
            B->>B: setStats(data)
        end
    and
        B->>N: GET /api/analytics/daily-stats?days=30
        N->>G: GET /analytics/daily-stats?days=30 (Bearer)
        G-->>N: DailyStats[]
        N-->>B: DailyStats[]
        B->>B: setDailyData (map field names)
    and
        B->>N: GET /api/analytics/geo-stats
        N->>G: GET /analytics/geo-stats (Bearer)
        G-->>N: GeoStat[]
        N-->>B: GeoStat[]
        B->>B: setGeoData(data)
    end

    B->>B: setLoading(false)
    B->>B: Render: KPIs + LineCharts + BarCharts + Costos
